message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE. The paper proposes a method for incorporating world knowledge into a neural question generation model, which falls under the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also evaluates the models on SQuAD and MS MARCO, which are datasets related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE).
